data.name: GoalLbl.Text
data.value: Our hope is to offer teachers and their students an easy way to practice math drills and keep track of progress. Helping the children is our first priority. We hope that we were able to provide a program that you find useful and a great addition to your classroom!

data.name: ProductLbl.Text
data.value:
Thanks for using our product! Raptor Math is intended for elementary school students who want a fun and interactive way to practice math problems. Raptor Math specifically focuses on addition and subtraction.
Teachers are able to customize their student's drills according to their skill level. Raptor Math also allows the Admin to view the current progress and statistics of each student.
